item.description:
fixed: <p>
The underlying problem has been fixed on the editor side in GB27947 for WordPress 5.7 (merged into core with <a class="closed ticket" href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/52394" title="#52394: defect (bug): Block Editor: Add defaultEditorStyles (closed: fixed)">#52394</a>).<br />
</p>
<p>
The left margin and padding added to these list elements by the editor will be reflected to the right side in RTL languages (in WordPress 5.7).<br />
</p>
<pre class="wiki">.editor-styles-wrapper ul,
.editor-styles-wrapper ol {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-left: 1.3em;
    margin-left: 1.3em;
}
</pre>
